+# PR-214 Reply Draft
+
+## T-214-01
+
+Addressed in [src/policy/preview.py](/private/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260423T232806Z_z7rdi_pj/20260423T232806Z-v4-multi-corpus-objective-run1/workspace/src/policy/preview.py:7) and [src/policy/approval_router.py](/private/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260423T232806Z_z7rdi_pj/20260423T232806Z-v4-multi-corpus-objective-run1/workspace/src/policy/approval_router.py:17). The fallback payload now preserves `approval_state` and `requires_human_review`, and the router normalizes `manual_review` to `human_review_required` before building the payload.
+
+## T-214-02
+
+Marked duplicate of `T-214-01`. The same reopened fallback regression was fixed by the payload and router changes above, so there was no separate code path to patch.
+
+## T-214-03
+
+Marked obsolete. This comment points at an outdated hunk and would revive legacy behavior on the current branch, so it was intentionally not applied.
+
+## T-214-04
+
+Addressed in [tests/test_preview.py](/private/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260423T232806Z_z7rdi_pj/20260423T232806Z-v4-multi-corpus-objective-run1/workspace/tests/test_preview.py:19). Added regression coverage for `preview_enabled=False`, including the `manual_review` normalization path through `build_policy_preview(...)`.
+
+## T-214-05
+
+Addressed in [docs/approval_policy.md](/private/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260423T232806Z_z7rdi_pj/20260423T232806Z-v4-multi-corpus-objective-run1/workspace/docs/approval_policy.md:9). The fallback example now shows `approval_state="human_review_required"` and `requires_human_review=true`.
